    2261hodge-theory-iii-5.2.4.1hodge-theory-iii-5.2.4.1.xmlEquation5.2.4.1hodge-theory-iii-5.2.4         a_*         = \varepsilon _* {a_\bullet }_*\colon          (X_\bullet )^\sim          \to  (S)^\sim .       \tag{5.2.4.1}

